	 VALUES(@QID,'','','n009331','02','4','7','0','2','1','2','0','0','2','',' <p>The nurse prepares oxytocin (Pitocin) for the client.  Which supplies will the nurse need to prepare the prescribed Pitocin solution?</p>
	<p><b>Select all that apply. </b></p>','<p>1) The best syringe to prepare this prescription is a 3 mL syringe.  A 5 mL syringe lacks the calibration to safely withdraw the appropriate amount medication.  </p>
