	 VALUES(@QID,'','','n009335','02','4','7','5','4','3','3','9','0','2','','<p>The nurse instructs a client newly diagnosed with type 1 diabetes about insulin.  Which statements, if made by the client to the nurse, demonstrate an understanding about insulin?</p>  <p><b>Select all that apply. </b></p>
