	<p>4) <b>CORRECT</b>— Often, people at risk for suicide more energy than they did previously, as they have made a decision and are working on following through with that decision. </p> 
	<p>5) <b>CORRECT</b>— Expressions of hopelessness and despair are possible warning signs of suicidal ideation.  </p>
	<p>6) While sleep deprivation is associated with depression, it s not a warning sign directly related to the risk for committing suicide.</p>
 
