	<p>6) While therapeutic communication is used in a group setting, it is used any time the nurse is communicating with the client.</p>
	','','1367','Therapeutic Communication','7','0',0,0,0,0,0,0,'','03','','','','','','','','','','','','','',1,-1,'E','','','','','','','','',0,0)

