	 VALUES(@QID,'','','n009339','02','3','5','1','4','3','3','3','0','7','',' <p>The nurse in the emergency department assesses a patient who reports a sudden onset of acute abdominal pain at a level of 9 out of 10. The patient requests to be medicated with meperidine (Demerol).  The same patient has been in the emergency department 5 times in the past 2 weeks.  The nurse is concerned that the patient is demonstrating drug-seeking behaviors.  Which notations in the patient’s chart support the nurse’s concern?  </p>
